...sihir gelap.

655
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,110
Ini tentang hidup dan mati,...

656
00:16:34,170 --> 00:16:35,940
...dan aku tidak ingin bermain sebagai Tuhan.

657
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:38,940
Jadi kamu malah membiarkan Dr. Morrison
berperan sebagai Tuhan.

658
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:52,570
Baunya enak kan?

659
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,960
Satu hal...

660
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:58,080
...yang ingin aku berikan putriku--

661
00:16:58,160 --> 00:17:01,550
...dia bisa menggoreng kaki ayam.

662
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:04,920
Aku membayangkan kau...
sedikit lapar...

663
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:09,560
...setelah 180 tahun dikubur.

664
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,810
Maka...

665
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:15,050
...kau mungkin tidak butuh makan,
karena abadi.

666
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,380
Tentu saja, kadang-kadang
kita cuma melakukan sesuatu karena...

667
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:20,520
...kita menikmatinya.

668
00:17:20,570 --> 00:17:22,860
Mau bicara?

669
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:27,160
Barusan kau bilang apa?

670
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:28,990
Yang mana?

671
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,580
Berapa lama?

672
00:17:30,660 --> 00:17:33,500
180 tahun.

673
00:17:33,570 --> 00:17:35,780
Mudah untuk lupa waktu,...

674
00:17:35,870 --> 00:17:37,090
...kurasa.

675
00:17:37,170 --> 00:17:40,290
Si jalang itu.

676
00:17:40,370 --> 00:17:42,210
Si jalang keji itu.

677
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:43,630
Siapa?

678
00:17:43,710 --> 00:17:46,080
Siapa yang melakukannya?

679
00:17:46,130 --> 00:17:48,630
Maksudku, mereka bilang kau diracuni, tapi...

680
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,630
...mereka jelas salah.

681
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,600
Aku ditipu.

682
00:17:52,690 --> 00:17:54,140
Oleh siapa?

683
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,040
{\an8}People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals (PETA) = Organisasi hak asasi binatang.

684
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:52,690
{\an8}United Way of America = Organisasi sosial untuk membantu sesama.

685
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:54,130
{\an8}Proses menjadikan seseorang menjadi santo.

686
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,610
{\an8}Maksudnya kemampuannya Zoe.

687
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:04,100
{\an8}Sabrina si remaja gila
Harusnya Sabrina the Teenage Witch = Sabrina si Penyihir Remaja.

688
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:10,050
{\an8}Penyihir/Dukun kulit hitam pertama, sekaligus budak di abad 17.

689
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:20,580
{\an8}Lagu Spiritual.

